item.title: Random Thoughts 3
item.description: (3:15 am, EST) Tonight was probably one of the worst nights yet – one of my project deadlines was pushed up one day, and that in addition to my fellowship application had to be done by tonight (11:59pm PST).

item.title: Random Thoughts 2
item.description: 2:13am After canceling my THIRD (research) meeting in this TEN week quarter, I’m becoming a bit scared – scared that I’ve become so ingrained in my undergrad habits that I’m having a hard time changing now.
